DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to determine the safety, tolerability and blood levels of AZD9742 after daily dosing for 14 days.
DOC.brief_title: A Study in Healthy Volunteers to Assess Safety and Blood Levels of AZD9742 After Multiple Doses Over 14 Days
DOC.criteria: BMI between 1930 Positive Fecal Occult Blood Test Prescriptions that inhibit liver function Received flu/H1N1 vaccine within 2 weeks before first dose
